linkParcel

  • linkParcel(container: IParcelInputContainer): FileParcel
    • Defined in ts/EdgeFileUploader.ts:528

    This is a very special function. When there are strange combinations of settings it could happen that although fileAPI-Support is disabled that we have a multi-upload. This is only possible in modern browsers if we force the fileAPI to not work. In this case a form with multiple-attribute enabled would upload multiple files at once. But only one upload-id would be provided per upload and with $n uploadfiles we would create $n FileParcels which ALL would trigger the form for themselves. That is why we need one main parcel and link all the others then.

    Parameters

    • container: IParcelInputContainer

      expects same data as container-Parameter in FileParcel constructor

    Returns FileParcel
